01:19:56.390 --> 01:19:59.470
in which the brain maintains longevity

01:19:59.470 --> 01:20:01.590
and maintains its ability to think.

01:20:01.590 --> 01:20:04.840
So we should all be seeking
optimal testosterone levels

01:20:04.840 --> 01:20:08.290
for ourselves, both
testosterone and estrogen.

01:20:08.290 --> 01:20:11.470
And many of the things that
we've discussed up until now,

01:20:11.470 --> 01:20:15.490
morning sunlight, exercise, fasting,

01:20:15.490 --> 01:20:18.670
those can support
testosterone and estrogen

01:20:18.670 --> 01:20:21.740
in meaningful and positive ways.

