and estrogen optimization.

01:20:31.460 --> 01:20:34.240
I just want to briefly
highlight two things

01:20:34.240 --> 01:20:35.620
that could be relevant,

01:20:35.620 --> 01:20:36.820
and then if you want more details,

01:20:36.820 --> 01:20:37.980
