02:04:14.290 --> 02:04:16.110
that support these practices.

02:04:16.110 --> 02:04:17.990
When I say "large bodies of work,"

02:04:17.990 --> 02:04:21.080
I'm a big fan of looking to
the scientific literature

02:04:21.080 --> 02:04:23.970
